{"word":"G2557 - κακοῦργος - kakoûrgos - kak-oor'-gos - Evil-doer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κακοῦργος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kakoûrgos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kak-oor'-gos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Evil-doer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"குற்றவாளி, துன்பத்தை அனுபவிக்கிறவன் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a malefactor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2556 - κακός - kakós - kak-os'/2556\">G2556</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G2041 - ἔργον - érgon - er'-gon/2041\">G2041</a>; a <i>wrong doer</i>, that is, <i>criminal:</i> - evil-doer, malefactor."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1573 - ἐκκακέω - ekkakéō - ek-kak-eh'-o/1573\">G1573</a>, <a href=\"#/G172 - ἄκακος - ákakos - ak'-ak-os/172\">G172</a>, <a href=\"#/G2549 - κακία - kakía - kak-ee'-ah/2549\">G2549</a>, <a href=\"#/G2550 - κακοήθεια - kakoḗtheia - kak-o-ay'-thi-ah/2550\">G2550</a>, <a href=\"#/G2554 - κακοποιέω - kakopoiéō - kak-op-oy-eh'-o/2554\">G2554</a>, <a href=\"#/G2555 - κακοποιός - kakopoiós - kak-op-oy-os'/2555\">G2555</a>, <a href=\"#/G2556 - κακός - kakós - kak-os'/2556\">G2556</a>, <a href=\"#/G2557 - κακοῦργος - kakoûrgos - kak-oor'-gos/2557\">G2557</a>, <a href=\"#/G420 - ἀνεξίκακος - anexíkakos - an-ex-ik'-ak-os/420\">G420</a>"}]}